high_descs: Turn left then walk straight to the stove
Pick up the pan on the stove
Turn left head to the counter
Put pan on the left side of the counter
Pick up the apple on the counter
Put the apple on the pan
Turn right then face the sink on the left
Pick up the knife on the sink
Turn left and face the counter
Slice the apple in the pan
anns.task_desc: Slice the apple in the pan

high_descs: Turn left and face the stove in front of you.
Take the pan off of the stove in front of you.
Turn left and face the top shelf of the counter in front of you.
Place the pan on the shelf in front of you.
Take the apple from the shelf in front of you.
Place the apple in the pan on the shelf in front of you.
Turn around and face the sink to your left.
Take the knife from the sink in front of you.
Turn left and face the apple on the pan on the shelf in front of you.
Slice the apple in the pan on the shelf in front of you.
anns.task_desc: Slice an apple in a pan on a shelf.

high_descs: Turn left and walk across the room to face the stove.
Pick up the pan on the left side of the stove.
Turn left and walk across the room to face the counter.
Place the pan on the back of the counter.
Pick up the apple on the counter.
Place the apple in the pan on the back of the counter.
Turn right and step forward to face the sink.
Pick up the knife on the sink.
Turn to the left and step forward to face the apple on the pan on the back of the counter.
Cut the apple in the pan into three slices.
anns.task_desc: To place an apple in a pan on the back of the counter as well as cut it into three slices.
